  </p>
  <table width="100%" style="margin:24px 0;"><tr><td align="center">
    <a href="{{payInvoiceUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;background:#ea580c;color:#fff;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">ชำระเงินตอนนี้</a>
  </td></tr></table>
  <p style="color:#777;font-size:14px;">ติดต่อสอบถาม: support@staysync.com</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background:#f9fafb;padding:16px;text-align:center;color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;">StaySync — Hotel Management</td></tr>
</table></td></tr></table></body></html>
